room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by The Ultimate Escape in Norwich
room_description: It was a great night for a walk. You and your friends decided to walk the trails in the woods when out of nowhere, an alien spaceship beamed you all up. You are now locked in a dissection room on their planet. You have to work together to signal NASA to rescue you all before time runs out and the aliens come back to dissect you all.
